{"tid":894733,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇samsung galaxy f 摺機","createTime":"2018-11-08T15:10:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T00:12:34.000Z","uid":78457,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c34f908ede3ab762a50d99d21ad7333fb4ac3a5e","tid":894733,"uid":78457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"Samsung Galaxy F 將會運行 One UI（操作介面），設有兩塊屏幕，日常使用是一部機面細小，可方便放入口袋的手機。機身外面會有一塊 4.6 AMOLED 屏幕，打開機身後，則為一塊 7.3 吋的屏幕，並支援 3 個 Apps 同時運行。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mhOyCxj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmhOyCxj.gif&h=ebfee63b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41fX4ct.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41fX4ct.png&h=6948b603&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7CT6Xxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7CT6Xxu.png&h=1cd5777e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n按照 Samsung 高層 Justin Denison 的說法，應用該屏幕的手機，將會在 2019 年發表，而從早前的傳聞， Samsung 於一月美國的 CES 展覽中較大機會發表。"},{"pid":"a422e2074569b758a7683dc1fcfc9cbf7d3257eb","tid":894733,"uid":7837,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:12:59.000Z","msg":"又好似幾正 可以帶著部tablet出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926ce80bce4c3cd4b1ff3d554a3d4354aae754a8","tid":894733,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"有人講cover個芒太細   好似好多空位<br />\n<br />\n螢幕infinity flex最高成本  新嘅PI物料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SECvEQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSECvEQG.jpg&h=c1fed7b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳聞零售價最低1500美金   最高2000美金"},{"pid":"1052655d061089fe67f66212b6f39dbcd5f66a5d","tid":894733,"uid":158977,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T15:23:44.000Z","msg":"lm等睇idog衝出嚟柒話好厚 唔知係